solution_code: public class Solution {--newline--    public List<String> readBinaryWatch(int num) {--newline--        List<String> times = new ArrayList<>();--newline--        for (int h=0; h<12; h++)--newline--            for (int m=0; m<60; m++)--newline--                if (Integer.bitCount(h * 64 + m) == num)--newline--                    times.add(String.format("%d:%02d", h, m));--newline--        return times;        --newline--    }--newline--}
